sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor Visitor
    participant Page as Testimonials Page<br/>(Astro SSG)
    participant Form as Comment Form<br/>(Astro Component)
    participant Worker as Cloudflare Worker<br/>(/api/comment)
    participant Sanity as Sanity API<br/>(api.sanity.io)
    participant Studio as Sanity Studio<br/>(CMS Dashboard)
    actor Owner as Site Owner
    participant CF as Cloudflare Pages<br/>(Build & Deploy)
    participant Site as Live Website<br/>(your-site.pages.dev)

    Note over Visitor,Site: PHASE 0: Feature Flag Check (Build Time)
    Note right of Page: PUBLIC_ENABLE_COMMENTS<br/>from astro:env/client

    alt PUBLIC_ENABLE_COMMENTS = true
        Page->>Form: Render CommentForm + CommentList
    else PUBLIC_ENABLE_COMMENTS = false
        Note right of Page: Form/List not rendered<br/>(static-only deployment)
    end

    Note over Visitor,Site: PHASE 1: Comment Submission

    Visitor->>Form: Fill out comment form
    Note right of Form: name, email (opt),<br/>comment text

    Visitor->>Form: Click Submit
    Form->>Worker: POST /api/comment<br/>(form data)

    activate Worker

    Worker->>Worker: Validate required fields
    alt Missing name or comment
        Worker-->>Form: 400 Bad Request (JSON)
        Note right of Form: Raw JSON response<br/>(Part C deferred)
    end

    Worker->>Worker: Check comment length
    alt Comment > 2000 chars
        Worker-->>Form: 400 Comment too long (JSON)
        Note right of Form: Raw JSON response<br/>(Part C deferred)
    end

    Worker->>Worker: Spam pattern detection
    Note right of Worker: Check for URLs,<br/>scripts, keywords
    alt Spam detected
        Worker-->>Form: 200 OK (silent reject)
        Form-->>Visitor: Show success (honeypot)
    end

    Worker->>Worker: Check honeypot field
    alt Honeypot filled (bot)
        Worker-->>Form: 200 OK (silent reject)
        Form-->>Visitor: Show success (honeypot)
    end

    Note over Visitor,Site: PHASE 2: Save to Sanity

    Worker->>Sanity: POST /data/mutate<br/>Create comment document
    Note right of Sanity: approved: false<br/>submittedAt: now()

    activate Sanity
    Sanity->>Sanity: Create document
    Sanity-->>Worker: 200 OK (document ID)
    deactivate Sanity

    Note right of Sanity: Email notification NOT IMPLEMENTED<br/>(future enhancement)

    Worker-->>Form: 303 Redirect<br/>/testimonials?submitted=true
    deactivate Worker

    Form-->>Visitor: Display success message<br/>"Thank you! Comment pending review."

    Note over Visitor,Site: PHASE 3: Moderation (async, Owner's schedule)

    Owner->>Studio: Login to Sanity Studio
    Studio->>Sanity: Fetch comments<br/>where approved == false
    Sanity-->>Studio: List of pending comments
    Studio-->>Owner: Display pending comments<br/>(○ prefix = unapproved)

    Owner->>Studio: Click comment to review
    Studio-->>Owner: Show full comment details

    alt Approve comment
        Owner->>Studio: Check "Approved" checkbox
        Owner->>Studio: Click Publish
        Studio->>Sanity: Update document<br/>approved: true
        Sanity-->>Studio: 200 OK
        Studio-->>Owner: Show ✓ (approved)
    else Reject as spam
        Owner->>Studio: Click (...) menu → Delete
        Studio->>Sanity: Delete document
        Sanity-->>Studio: 200 OK
        Studio-->>Owner: Comment removed
    end

    Note over Visitor,Site: PHASE 4: Deploy to Live Site

    Owner->>CF: Trigger deployment<br/>(Dashboard or CLI)
    activate CF

    CF->>Sanity: Fetch all content<br/>(build-time query)
    Note right of CF: *[_type == "comment"<br/>&& approved == true]
    Sanity-->>CF: Approved comments

    CF->>CF: Astro build<br/>(generate static HTML)
    CF->>CF: Deploy to CDN<br/>(edge locations)
    CF-->>Owner: Deployment complete
    deactivate CF

    Note over Visitor,Site: PHASE 5: Comment Visible

    Visitor->>Site: Visit testimonials page
    Site-->>Visitor: Page with approved comments<br/>(including their comment)
